name: COMPETE T-Shirt
description:
Our current product is the COMPETE t-shirt, which sells for $20.

It is a unique design with a portrait of USC football Coach Pete Carroll and the word “COMPETE” written under his image. This t-shirt is meant to symbolize the spirit of Trojan football and our appreciation of Pete Carroll.

All t-shirts are printed on high-quality American Apparel shirt blanks.

***Only deliveries in the USC area are currently being accepted. You may also arrange to pick up your t-shirt at USC. All deliveries and pick ups will be in person.***

If you have any questions, please contact us at fighton4charity@gmail.com
